 rming story of Maria and the von Trapp family is a celebration of love\, c
 ourage\, and the power of music.&nbsp\; A must-see for audiences of all ag
 es!&nbsp\;&nbsp\;\n\nTicket Sales \n\n&nbsp\;\n\nPerformance at the Semino
 le Theatre:\n&nbsp\;\n\n\n	April 4\, 2025&nbsp\; |&nbsp\; 7:00 PM\n	April 
